 varying light conditions. The dual I2 sensors provide the Soldier with depth perception for ease of low-light level maneuvers and the ability to detect rifle-mounted aiming lights to engage targets. The ENVG-B
 can also be operated in a monocular configuration by moving one of the two individually rotating monoculars. The ENVG-B has a near infrared (NIR) emitting light source that provides illumination for close-up
