 (CIAT) and Surface Training Program Combat System (STP-CS) (formerly Surface Advanced Virtual Environment Combat System (STAVE-CS)). These systems provide a coordinated stimulation/simulation of
 shipboard combat systems to facilitate combat systems team training, forming the backbone of a world-class Fleet's training pipeline, providing the capability to conduct realistic joint warfare training across the
 spectrum of armed conflict, and conduct realistic unit level team training in all primary warfare areas. Hardware and software upgrades including Infrastructure as a Service (IaaS) and shipboard ECS are required
