 procurement and installation of hardware and software at the applicable C-ARTS sites and Centers of Excellence in Norfolk, Great Lakes, and at SWOS Newport. Class training simulators and equipment include
 the following: Advanced Weapons Elevators (AWEs), Machinery Control and Monitoring System (MCMS), Federated Machinery Local Area Network (FMLAN)/ Machinery Local Area Network (MLAN), Aircraft
 Landing and Recovery Equipment (ALRE) Jet Blast Deflector (JBD) Electromechanical Actuators, Emergency Diesel Generators (EDGs), Modular Refrigeration Units (MRU), Steering Gear Control Systems
 (SGCS), Zonal Electrical Distribution System (ZEDS), Vacuum Collection Holding Transfer (VCHT), Plasma Arc Waste Destruction System (PAWDS),Weapons Elevator and Stores Elevator Electromechanical
